column10: How POSITIVE do you feel right now?
column11: How NEGATIVE do you feel right now?
column19: Right now, I feel like difficulties are piling up so high I cannot overcome them.
column21: How would you rate your quality of sleep last night?
column22: How many hours and minutes of sleep did you get last night? This may be different from the number of hours spent in bed.
column23: How long did you spend awake at night? This includes the time it took to fall asleep and awakenings from sleep.
